<div><strong>STORY HIGHLIGHTS</strong></div>
<ul class="cnn_bulletbin cnnStryHghLght">
<!--google_ad_section_start-->
<li>Legalizing drug use is a bad idea, Pope Francis says</li>
<li>"There can be no yielding or compromise" to the evil of drugs, he says</li>
<li>Public sentiment isn't with him; most Americans at least now favor legalization</li>
<li>Uruguay recently legalized marijuana, and Jamaica is set to decriminalize it soon</li>
<!--google_ad_section_end-->
</ul>
</div></div>
<div class="cnn_strylftcntnt adtag15090">
